{% from "components/eesti-isikukood-view/macro.njk" import eestiIsikukoodView %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<dl>
  <dt>Personal Identification Code</dt>
  <dd>{{ eestiIsikukoodView({ value: "sample-value", label: "Personal Identification Code" }) }}</dd>
</dl>

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>11 digits in the form GYYMMDDSSSC: G is sex and century (odd male, even female; 1-2 19th c., 3-4 20th c., 5-6 21st c.), SSS distinguishes persons born the same day, C is a checksum.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_identification_number#Estonia">Personal Identification Code</a>.</p>
